## MuPDF

MuPDF is not bundled, linked, downloaded, or required by the default workspace
build. The fake shim remains the default backend.

The opt-in `real-mupdf` Milestone 1 developer path is pinned to MuPDF 1.27.2,
announced in the official MuPDF release history on 2026-02-20. The selected
source archive is:

<https://casper.mupdf.com/downloads/archive/mupdf-1.27.2-source.tar.gz>

MuPDF is used under AGPL-3.0 for this project. No local MuPDF patches are
currently recorded.

For any distributed binary or network service that enables `real-mupdf`, the
corresponding source must include this workspace, the C shim, build scripts, the
exact MuPDF 1.27.2 source archive above, all bundled third-party notices from
that source tree, and any local patches. The source-offer template is
`docs/compliance/agpl-source-offer.md`.

## Rust Toolchain

The Milestone 0 default workspace build currently depends only on the Rust
standard library and local workspace crates.

Optional post-M0 features may add third-party crates to `Cargo.lock`. They are
not part of the default M0 resolve graph unless their feature is enabled. Before
any optional feature becomes a required build or shipped distribution target,
this file must be regenerated to include that feature's exact third-party
dependency notices.

